headline: Workday, Inc. (WDAY) Launches Subsidiary for U.S. Government; Partners with Seattle University
summary: Workday, Inc. (NASDAQ:WDAY) secures a place on our list of the 12 Best Ethical Companies to Invest in 2025. On July 14, 2025, Workday, Inc. (NASDAQ:WDAY) was selected by Seattle University as its partner.
